              <Culture>en-GB</Culture>
              <Text> ============================================================
 BlockParam Demo - Process Plant Structure
 Author: Tobias Laubscher
 Target: TIA Portal V17+

 Import as external source (SCL). Types compile in order:
   UDT_AlarmLimits -> UDT_ControlValve -> UDT_EquipmentModule
   -> UDT_ProcessUnit -> DB_ProcessPlant_A1

 Hierarchy depth from DB root to leaf:
   DB -> units[] -> modules[] -> valves[] -> *Limits -> hiLimit  (5 levels)

 Scale:
   2 Units x 3 Modules x 4 Valves = 24 Valves
   24 Valves x 2 Limit blocks      = 48 Alarm blocks
   48 Alarm blocks x 4 limits      = 192 limit members
 ============================================================</Text>
